  m_Name: Self-Promotion
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::FlightPaper.ProjectSorrow.Encounters.EncounterScriptableObject
  id: 5
  title: Self-Promotion
  description: 'A local event planner approaches you with an offer.


    There''s
    a couple of opportunities coming up that could use some talent. One is an ad
    for a somewhat questionable company. Another is an annual charity fundraiser.


    He
    pushes you to agree to one and won''t take no for an answer. '
  options:
  - title: Sell out for the ad
    description: <color=green>+$30</color>, <color=red>-15</color> reputation
    requirement: 
    conclusion: 'Despite the company''s reputation, you agree to do the ad for some
      extra cash.


      Unfortunately, some of your peers overhear this deal. As
      you walk away, you can see the real look of disappointment on their faces.'
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: Reputation
  - title: Agree to help with the charity
    description: <color=#A1740E>+10</color> reputation, <color=red>-$20</color>
    requirement: Requires <color=green>$20</color>
    conclusion: "You agree to help with the charity and donate some money. \n\nEveryone
      liked that."
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: Reputation
  - title: Host the charity event
    description: <color=#A1740E>+20</color> reputation, lose <color=#00C300>Giant
      Check</color>
    requirement: 
    conclusion: 'Seizing the opportunity, you suggest hosting the charity event.


      The
      event planner loves the idea and starts exclaiming his excitement. The people
      around you even start clapping.


      Everyone really liked that.'
    isHidden: 1
    item: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 25f1774ba621fbd43b6f793c7caaad52, type: 2}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: 
  minRound: 0
